  "id": "019cdcdc-fd01-7d11-b0d7-9b1601bf4403",
  "content": "### D72: Cross-File Import Resolution via Cargo.toml Module Tree\n### D73: Markdown AST Cross-References via pulldown-cmark\n\n### D74: Declaration + Usage Tracking in Chunking Pipeline\n- **Decision:** Two-pass post-processing in `discover_cross_file_relations()` to find type/trait definitions and their cross-file usages, creating `\"uses\"` edges\n- **Scope:** `corvia-kernel` crate (`ChunkingPipeline`)\n- **Rationale:** The most impactful change for graph density. When `QueryableStore` is defined in `traits.rs` and used in 4 store implementations, those edges should exist.\n\n\n### D75: Lazy Search-Time Edge Discovery (deferred to M4.1)\n- **Decision:** Deferred. At search time, discover missing edges and persist them for future queries. Not needed for M3.4 — ingest-time fixes will create sufficient graph density.\n- **Rationale:** Adds write operations to read path, complexity not justified until ingest-time edges are validated.\n\n---\n",
